{"tid":159252,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想養貓","createTime":"2017-03-17T00:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T13:25:53.000Z","uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc44f80e55f3e8f564b8fd3763c17b2484350db3","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:05:08.000Z","msg":"首先係一定會去領養，有冇邊間好啲？<br />\n<br />\n問過朋友要買貓沙、貓抓板、裝貓網（想問下晾衫用窗口點算？裝左咪無得晾衫？但唔裝我又驚佢會突然飛出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）、會買寵物保險（有冇建議？）、會買啲噴霧去噴梳化（仲有冇其他方法去防止佢抓爛梳化？）、預備大膠兜裝貓沙，仲有冇其他需要準備？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，仲有啲咩野要考慮？<br />\n朋友話要俾佢抓爛衫，但我諗我應該無問題，一來我無咩貴衫，二來衫爛可以再買。<br />\n朋友再話可能會俾佢咬，我諗我應該ok，男子漢大丈夫怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">除非佢咬我巨龍啦<del></del></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽講唔可以帶貓出街？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細佬我未養過任何寵物，但一直都好鍾意貓貓，想做好萬全既準備先去領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad3080467744212f29d35165179f2ea2645d6cd","tid":159252,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:08:16.000Z","msg":"貓窗，一定要<br />\n糧，百佳糧<br />\n唔用貓砂用報紙，或者教佢去馬桶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請支持港短"},{"pid":"a234eca7ef7efbcd872af7977558cd40979f5ea2","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓窗，一定要<br />\n糧，百佳糧<br />\n唔用貓砂用報紙，或者教佢去馬桶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請支持港短</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓窗姐係d人講既裝係窗度既網？<br /