唔可以帶貓出街？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細佬我未養過任何寵物，但一直都好鍾意貓貓，想做好萬全既準備先去領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貓窗用防蚊沙窗就得 主要都係防止主子跳樓"},{"pid":"fa16efa1aca4f60afa598bbe3b82ced7535a729d","tid":159252,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏左，會絕育<br />\n<br />\n同埋一開始既野要預幾多錢左右？</blockquote><br />\n囡仔貴d 好似過千<br />\n男仔就近一千<br />\n利申 冇幫主子絕育以保雄風"},{"pid":"ef83134e5d942c8745767ae6acba81915f9637b3","tid":159252,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏左，會絕育<br />\n<br />\n同埋一開始既野要預幾多錢左右？</blockquote><br />\n都係唔好養我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30633ae0dd6890b9789d867014902a37c624c92","tid":159252,"uid":1611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2f66626f2e5dd5fee8412dfeb5de9bb02ad343","tid":159252,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:55:18.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得如果要養喵<br />\n領養一隻細喵開始會比較好<br />\n不過細喵初初係會叫到好嘈<br />\n除此之外可以睇住喵仔成長同埋互相感情都深厚d<br />\n雖然咁講好對唔住等緊人養既大喵"},{"pid":"f9adb2880dfd0d9d9163f7b2e229ecfa3f665cac","tid":159252,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"金屬活動窗網<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/100124_72f3f44bda63facd9a6b7545711497aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F100124_72f3f44bda63facd9a6b7545711497aa.jpg&h=d8742a51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a17495632b58d9de44f941ab86f0c2e7fa257b7a","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講漏左，會絕育<br />\n<br />\n同埋一開始既野要預幾多錢左右？</blockquote><br />\n都係唔好養我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7791b23337b1e3925587c0699f40b7f85366c492","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己覺得如果要養喵<br />\n領養一隻細喵開始會比較好<br />\n不過細喵初初係會叫到好嘈<br />\n除此之外可以睇住喵仔成長同埋互相感情都深厚d<br />\n雖然咁講好對唔住等緊人養既大喵</blockquote><br />\n我都係打算領養細喵，有幾細得幾細。<br />\n<br />\n我唔想養佢5、6年就離開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bc6af7eceaf48c1ddcba7e79258e328b5066a8","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金屬活動窗網<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/100124_72f3f44bda63facd9a6b7545711497aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F100124_72f3f44bda63facd9a6b7545711497aa.jpg&h=d8742a51&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會好難裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e22a09fcf21ee48c5d40847104e650c84629cc","tid":159252,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"絕育我去愛協的<br />\n男仔$200<br />\n女仔$300 因爲女仔要開肚仔<br />\n其實唔記得幾錢總之唔貴"},{"pid":"9fc1f4a520bd7ee49c27eab3f465f2c99e1897c1","tid":159252,"uid":49651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"那以後就來養貓吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99cd1abcc359edc374cafca0b5d7b7fe51