0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8c6ec2d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打索性換窗花會好啲，又唔貴<br />\n又美觀又可以晾衫<br />\n近年出左啲透明嘅寵物窗花直情係無得彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，巴打可以係群貓會睇下有無岩眼緣嘅<br />\n好多都打哂針，絕左育，比五百就得"},{"pid":"37ed4acabb899b210a01095e64d86d8830a9a45f","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"其實我自己多數係房，唔俾佢出廳會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00409effdf7259cb9398acea65c4a71c3578ffd","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8c6ec2d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打索性換窗花會好啲，又唔貴<br />\n又美觀又可以晾衫<br />\n近年出左啲透明嘅寵物窗花直情係無得彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，巴打可以係群貓會睇下有無岩眼緣嘅<br />\n好多都打哂針，絕左育，比五百就得</blockquote><br />\n返屋企去睇下，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9749784d7006648859dba8290eb43aba184087f5","tid":159252,"uid":82621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"