i\" />"},{"pid":"eb8feb6b76103aef3f613a96a043d45ffa726d3e","tid":159252,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓窗，一定要<br />\n糧，百佳糧<br />\n唔用貓砂用報紙，或者教佢去馬桶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請支持港短</blockquote><br />\n百佳糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前啲人唔係話貓仔去馬桶大小便唔係幾好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2b70cf0382ba3e03f1c61f35cf0c6a754f8a47","tid":159252,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JJ915S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JJ915S.jpg&h=3035fee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43221a4ba55744fccf54933c32a5a56ca295c79","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過人講可以用檸檬汁溝水噴落沙發到 因為貓貓唔中意浸味 不過唔知work唔work<br />\n可以買啲貓抓板 再唔係自製都得 有啲麻繩圍住凳腳枱腳咁綁實 再放少少貓草引貓仔去磨爪<br />\n我都想養貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係未諗掂窗網點搞</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20071202000051KK03226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20071202000051KK03226&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a44a1490\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20071202000051KK03226</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗住到時搵呢條link講果枝噴霧"},{"pid":"38fcc498ea808bfdc529705adf6e359536f189bc","tid":159252,"uid":30568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b912a80ad858f5107936ad3b308791c06d110371","tid":159252,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"愛協領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶齊住址證明同窗網相睇中嘅貓無人hold醫生睇過健康可即日拎"},{"pid":"2e1fc6d6926566ffe931b32e6db76c51d9507062","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"又群貓會又愛協，去邊度領養好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be700ce31080d0aa4eea70900aa9c51f8690156a","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02434cd677f4dc38e900645a9710bc7bedb9728d","tid":159252,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"我都想隻貓識自己上廁所開大<br />\n啲指甲老泥屎臭撚到呢<br />\n仲要撥到啲沙周圍都係"},{"pid":"51fad25122e3d343ac9e3ffd9bf2271f92371b67","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又群貓會又愛協，去邊度領養好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n群貓會好撚麻煩<br />\n我朋友正正常常女仔一個<br />\n領養完後話以後唔會再去，麻7煩咁話<br />\n<br />\n愛協好似聽落好d<br />\n朋友領養過<br />\n貓勁乖 （因為貓有攻擊性/唔易養好快會畀愛協放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n畀完500（？唔太記得）攞完乾手淨腳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持樓主<br />\n<br />\n可以考慮下大貓呀<br />\n貓平均都有1x 幾歲命<br />\n大貓都有排養"},{"pid":"085a5a9c709be831af58d62326db710324435fca","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己"},{"pid":"38a7e962d24f40dc4f6162da72da3df68402438f","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想隻貓識自己上廁所開大<br />\n啲指甲老泥屎臭撚到呢<br />\n仲要撥到啲沙周圍都係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n指甲老泥好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2284037099649599fb8720525ef57d797d3cdf6","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"樓主最好準備埋指甲鉗<br />\n<br />\n貓間中要剪指甲<br />\n抓親你都唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n平既12蚊店就有（不過都幾廢）<br />\n貴既100-200度"},{"pid":"0db51717920c20a2e27180e77770cbeec7bf186e","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4309af0ea94b6d252470a04050db6bf3cc87d3aa","tid":159252,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用誠意打動佢<br />\n每日同佢講有關養貓既嘢<br />\n話佢知你好有心養"},{"pid":"616fae2ccb5c96a8c9e96751bfdc19050ec1a1a6","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓屎貓尿唔會周圍飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有貓砂盤架嘛"},{"pid":"5b69eca24e018b07bb3cdbdc6ab1bef0c33b4505","tid":159252,"uid":47512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c79df803e0b7974a7016fcce38f14c7107338e6","tid":159252,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用誠意打動佢<br />\n每日同佢講有關養貓既嘢<br />\n話佢知你好有心養</blockquote><br />\n開頭寫包單話所以野會自己負責，話唔會俾佢出黎阻到啊媽，帶左主人入屋先<br />\n之後慢慢就會俾主人感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好老實o既 養貓預咗污糟<br />\n佢成日爬上我張床抹屎<br />\n我睇到張床頭有啲屎漬都嬲嬲地<br />\n咁可以點姐 養得佢就一世<br />\n仲有啲貓毛 係咁甩<br />\n個廁所比佢啲屎尿搞到成日要開抽氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad36d3a1d4baf7077365a7f78074c6a06cf57bec","tid":159252,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用誠意打動佢<br />\n每日同佢講有關養貓既嘢<br />\n話佢知你好有心養</blockquote><br />\n開頭寫包單話所以野會自己負責，話唔會俾佢出黎阻到啊媽，帶左主人入屋先<br />\n之後慢慢就會俾主人感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好老實o既 養貓預咗污糟<br />\n佢成日爬上我張床抹屎<br />\n我睇到張床頭有啲屎漬都嬲嬲地<br />\n咁可以點姐 養得佢就一世<br />\n仲有啲貓毛 係咁甩<br />\n個廁所比佢啲屎尿搞到成日要開抽氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你隻咁污糟既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n養過幾隻，佢地都好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0637169ecb15a80e47a2a1d97035b211c09c03","tid":159252,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8c6ec2d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打索性換窗花會好啲，又唔貴<br />\n又美觀又可以晾衫<br />\n近年出左啲透明嘅寵物窗花直情係無得彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，巴打可以係群貓會睇下有無岩眼緣嘅<br />\n好多都打哂針，絕左育，比五百就得</blockquote><br />\n返屋企去睇下，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/213954_07679820547d031b1e7f057fc12d649e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F213954_07679820547d031b1e7f057fc12d649e.jpg&h=6347c422&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98e7dbb63783ddb65c06511605ff97637b5c2f7","tid":159252,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果困佢係房同籠，唔俾佢出廳既話會唔會好衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下間房幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好唔好困住佢啦<br />\n將心比己</blockquote><br />\n頭先同老母講，佢話怕d貓屎貓尿周圍飛，唔俾我養。<br />\n此post已完⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用誠意打動佢<br />\n每日同佢講有關養貓既嘢<br />\n話佢知你好有心養</blockquote><br />\n開頭寫包單話所以野會自己負責，話唔會俾佢出黎阻到啊媽，帶左主人入屋先<br />\n之後慢慢就會俾主人感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n養左幾隻，因為有寵物比打理得以前更乾淨<br />\n<br />\n驚空氣太多貓毛你就買部空氣清新機，我老母一樣一開頭唔鐘意，結果而家所有野都唔使我俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d35793448cae65e50aec9b85d86188742eb5db","tid":159252,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.catsocietyhk.org%2Fcat-knowledge%2Fwindow-safety%2F%3Fmobile%3D1&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8c6ec2d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catsocietyhk.org/cat-knowledge/window-safety/?mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打索性換窗花會好啲，又唔貴<br />\n又美觀又可以晾衫<br />\n近年出左啲透明嘅寵物窗花直情係無得彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，巴打可以係群貓會睇下有無岩眼緣嘅<br />\n好多都打哂針，絕左育，比五百就得</blockquote><br />\n返屋企去睇下，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/213954_07679820547d031b1e7f057fc12d649e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F213954_07679820547d031b1e7f057fc12d649e.jpg&h=6347c422&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks 但養貓計劃可能要hold住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}